<bibRefCitation author="Kailola, P. J." box="[846,1015,223,248]" pageId="238" pageNumber="239" pagination="1 - 277" refId="ref190004" refString="Kailola, P. J. (1975) A catalogue of the fish reference collection at the Kanudi Fisheries Research Laboratory, Port Moresby. Department of Agriculture, Stock &amp; Fisheries, Port Moresby, Research Bulletin, 16, 1 - 277." type="journal article" year="1975">Kailola (1975</bibRefCitation>
